@startuml seq_11_edit_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-11 Edit Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary

User -> Frontend: Click edit post
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/posts/{id}
Controller -> Service: Get Post
Service -> PostRepo: Find post by ID
PostRepo --> Service: Post Data
Service --> Controller: Post Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display edit form

User -> Frontend: Modify content & change media
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/posts/{id} (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: Update Post
Service -> PostRepo: Verify post ownership
PostRepo --> Service: Ownership confirmed

alt Old media marked for removal
    Service -> Cloudinary: Delete media by Public ID
    Cloudinary --> Service: Deletion confirmed
end

alt New media attached
    Service -> Cloudinary: Upload new media stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> PostRepo: Update Post record in DB
PostRepo --> Service: Post updated
Service --> Controller: Updated Post Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Show updated post
@enduml